    "question_id" : 10971968,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I not be able to find squid number in sonar 5.6, with this annotation also works:</p>\n\n<pre><code>@SuppressWarnings({\"pmd:AvoidCatchingGenericException\", \"checkstyle:com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.checks.coding.IllegalCatchCheck\"})\n</code></pre>\n"
